                <note rend="inline" type="source">463.00 R 29/171: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in France</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Herrick</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1925-03-03T12:00:00+00:00">
                            <hi rend="italic">March 3, 1925—noon</hi>
                        </date>.<lb/>[Received March 3—11:02 a.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>150. Your 99, February 24, 4 p.m. Memorandum was presented to the Conference of
                    Ambassadors at its 275th meeting this morning. No comment was made but it was
                    reserved for future discussion.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Herrick</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
